Business Talk with Michael Avery is South Africa’s leading online business talk show – and your executives can take part in it. As part of BusinessTech, Business Talk has excellent interview packages which allow your executives to get featured on the show. This offers unmatched exposure to a highly-influential business audience, and lets your executives share their thought leadership insights. All Business Talk interviews are published to the Business Talk website, BusinessTech, YouTube, Facebook, and Spotify – reaching an engaged audience. Business Talk has been well received since launch, with the show hosted by highly-respected radio and TV personality Michael Avery. Avery is well known in business circles for his roles on Classic FM and Business Day TV – and as the anchor of the HOT Business show on HOT 1027. Guests on the show have included the biggest names in the South African business space, including Andrew Golding, chief executive of the Pam Golding Property group; Sim Tshabalala, joint chief executive of the Standard Bank Group; Magda Wierzycka, co-founder of Sygnia; Michael Jordaan, co-founder of Bank Zero and founder of Montegray Capital; and many more business leaders. To find out more about taking part in Business Talk, contact BusinessTech’s advertising team.